    <div align="center"><h1>Effects of Rooms on Voice and Music</h1></div>

This page is designed to show you how a room affects the sound of voice and music.  Below you will find a number of different music and speech samples as they would sound in different environments.  For example, to compare speech in several environments you would click on the links in the column labeled Speech.<p>

<H3> Warning!  While the samples are in .mp3 format, some of them are still quite large files (>500k) which might take a while to load</h3>




